{"tid":1439673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家利用林奠嘅言論幫運動做文宣","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:51:56.000Z","uid":126783,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92d595bdab189a5154c655cc6850d8355e0d25bc","tid":1439673,"uid":126783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"林奠係8月9 日嘅記者會用到THEY HAVE NO STAKE IN SOCIETY<br />\n意思係在社會無貢獻嘅人<br />\n<br />\n咁我地就可以幫佢界定下邊尐人可以歸類入去啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 未開始出來工作嘅年輕人<br />\n2. 拎綜援嘅低收入家庭<br />\n3. 拎綜援嘅傷健人士<br />\n4. 無需交稅嘅一般市民<br />\n5. 新香港人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由於你地對社會無貢獻, <br />\n所以你就無權係社會發聲<br />\n所以你地就無權去講政府做得唔岩<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">所以警察扑你個頭係天經地義<br />\n所以俾黑社會斬都係理所當然</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n再點樣上綱上線大家咁聰明自己來啦<br />\n聽日深水埗就正正對準晒上面嘅人<br />\n文宣要嘅係挑起佢地對政府嘅憤怒同恐懼"},{"pid":"e0414490f454f77b72cedad4341b799650d859f8","tid":1439673,"uid":126783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"ecbb721417bd5d4b1b08f4b09ea8d02c72e6ba0a","tid":1439673,"uid":126783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"8d606527e391051e1d59392c56d7603d7975a533","tid":1439673,"uid":126783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f91650eafb4edc9e57de3ff377f8e18d2d3f3478","tid":1439673,"uid":126783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"1e43955259fbbac3c1c20739da37278b35b36fd5","tid":1439673,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It is now or never</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbRLHyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3